basisset.dc:description: Partridge Uncontracted Basis Sets --------------------------------- Elements Reference Li, Be: (16s) H. Partridge, J. Chem. Phys. 90, 1043 (1989). B - Ne: (16s,11p) Na - Mg: (19s,11p) H. Partridge, J. Chem. Phys. 87, 6643 (1987). Al - Ar: (18s,13p) K - Ca: (22s,14p) Sc (22s,16p,8d) Ti (22s,14p,9d) V (22s,14p,10d) Mn - Fe: (22s,15p,11d) Co (22s,15p,8d) Ni (22s,15p,11d) Cu (22s,14p,10d) Zn (22s,15p,8d) Ga (21s,16p,11d) Ge (21s,16p,10d) These are groundstate, RHF energy-optimized, uncontracted basis sets. This set is one of the smaller sets of uncontracted, energy-optimized primitives published by H. Partridge. The MSRC basis set library contains small, intermediate and large Partridge basis sets.
